  "name": "HWH International Inc.",
  "description": "HWH International Inc. engages in the food and beverage business in Singapore and South Korea. The company provides Hapi Caf\u00e9, a health-focused dining destination offering a various nutritious meal, including Keto and plant-based options; Hapi Marketplace, a business-to-consumer platform featuring diverse product categories; and Hapi Wealth Builder, an educational program focused on wealth-building strategies; and provides participants the opportunity to attend courses, workshops, and coaching sessions in person fostering a collaborative learning environment for those dedicated to learning about investment in equities and wealth-building strategies. The company was founded in 2021 and is based in Bethesda, Maryland.",
